summary: Celebrating that I’ll be meeting my best friend in #reptourlondon in just 7 days and that I’d do it over and over again if I...
caption:
Celebrating that I’ll be meeting my best friend in #reptourlondon in just 7 days and that I’d do it over and over again if I could! Here’s a cover of “I’m only me when I’m with you” to prove that @taylorswift’s old songs are just as amazing as the new ones. I love them all!!!
This was the first song that I played to my boyfriend. He told me he knew it and I was so so so impressed! He said that Taylor was an amazing singer-songwriter and he made my whole year! One of the reasons that we’re together is because he puts up with my crazy Taylor obsession, quotes her songs and basically doesn’t dump me when I’m talking about her 24/7. He’ll be attending night 2 with me!!!
Taylor, I’m only up when you’re not down, so let’s hug in London to prove to each other that we’re doing better than we ever were!!! I’d be wonderstruck blushing all the way back to Spain if that happened!! 💖💖💖
@taylornation
